NoiseRemover - NoiseRemover中的类
The NoiseRemover class provides a Java interface to the M-functions from the files: D:\\code\\repository\\Denoising\\code2\\PA.m D:\\code\\repository\\Denoising\\code2\\RemovalNoise.m The NoiseRemover.dispose() method must be called on a NoiseRemover instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed.

NoiseRemoverRemote - NoiseRemover中的接口
The NoiseRemoverRemote class provides a Java RMI-compliant interface to the M-functions from the files: D:\\code\\repository\\Denoising\\code2\\PA.m D:\\code\\repository\\Denoising\\code2\\RemovalNoise.m The dispose() method must be called on a NoiseRemoverRemote instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed, and the server-side proxy is unexported.
